outside the conservancy areas,

00:07:17.090 --> 00:07:19.590
hanging out with cows
and all kinds of stuff.

00:07:19.590 --> 00:07:21.020
But zebras are a--

00:07:21.020 --> 00:07:21.740
who love zebras?

